"},{"text":"Joystick","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Joystick view used to control various activities such as moving a character on the screen.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The View creates a Rectangular region to act as a hitbox for drag gestures. Once a drag"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is initiated the joystick appears on screen centered at the start location of the gesture. While"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dragging, the thumb of the joystick is limited be within the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"radius"},{"type":"text","text":" of the sticks background circle."}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"Joystick"}}}